msgstr "Activé"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1403
msgid "Disabled"
msgstr "Désactivé"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1409
msgid ""
"Forced ON by the AGNOSIS_DEBUG constant in wp-config.php — the checkbox "
"above has no effect until that line is removed."
msgstr ""
"FORCÉ SUR ON par la constante AGNOSIS_DEBUG dans wp-config.php — la case à "
"cocher ci-dessus n’a aucun effet tant que cette ligne n’est pas supprimée."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1411
msgid ""
"Forced OFF by the AGNOSIS_DEBUG constant in wp-config.php — the checkbox "
"above has no effect until that line is removed."
msgstr ""
"FORCÉ SUR OFF par la constante AGNOSIS_DEBUG dans wp-config.php — la case à "
"cocher ci-dessus n’a aucun effet tant que cette ligne n’est pas supprimée."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1419
msgid "Directory"
msgstr "Répertoire"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1422
msgid "Filter with agnosis_debug_dir to redirect debug output elsewhere."
msgstr ""
"Filtrez avec agnosis_debug_dir pour rediriger la sortie de débogage "
"ailleurs."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1429
msgid ".txt file(s) in the directory"
msgstr "fichier(s) .txt dans le répertoire"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1435
msgid ""
"Delete all .txt files in the debug directory? The directory itself stays in "
"place so future debug writes still land cleanly."
msgstr ""
"Supprimer tous les fichiers .txt du répertoire de débogage ? Le répertoire "
"lui-même reste en place afin que les futures écritures de débogage s’y "
"déposent correctement."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1440
msgid "Clear Debug Files"
msgstr "Effacer les fichiers de débogage"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1471
msgid "Term Translation Cache"
msgstr "Cache de traduction des termes"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1475
msgid "Cached translations"
msgstr "Traductions en cache"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1478
msgid ""
"AI-translated tag/medium term names, cached so the same term always gets the"
" same translated label instead of a fresh AI phrasing per post. Renaming a "
"term already clears its own cached entry automatically; use the button below"
" only if a cached translation itself is wrong."
msgstr ""
"Noms de termes de tag / média traduits par IA, mis en cache afin que le même"
" terme obtienne toujours le même libellé traduit au lieu d’une nouvelle "
"formulation IA à chaque publication. Renommer un terme efface déjà "
"automatiquement sa propre entrée en cache ; utilisez le bouton ci-dessous "
"uniquement si une traduction en cache est elle-même erronée."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1484
msgid ""
"Clear every cached term translation? Nothing is deleted from your site — "
"terms will simply be re-translated by AI the next time they're needed."
msgstr ""
"Effacer toutes les traductions de termes en cache ? Rien ne sera supprimé de"
" votre site — les termes seront simplement retraduits par l’IA la prochaine "
"fois qu’ils seront nécessaires."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1489
msgid "Clear Term Translation Cache"
msgstr "Effacer le cache de traduction des termes"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1521
msgid "Pipeline Logs"
msgstr "Journaux du pipeline"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1526
msgid "Clear all log entries?"
msgstr "Effacer toutes les entrées du journal ?"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1527
msgid "Clear All"
msgstr "Tout effacer"

#. translators: %d: total log entry count
#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1536
#, php-format
msgid ""
"%d entries total. Logs are pruned automatically according to the Inbox "
"retention setting."
msgstr ""
"%d entrées au total. Les journaux sont purgés automatiquement selon le "
"paramètre de rétention de la boîte de réception."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1543
msgid "No log entries yet."
msgstr "Aucune entrée de journal pour le moment."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1548
msgid "Time"
msgstr "Heure"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1549
msgid "Level"
msgstr "Niveau"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1550
msgid "Context"
msgstr "Contexte"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1623
msgid "Inbox Tools"
msgstr "Outils de boîte de réception"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1627
msgid "Test connection"
msgstr "Tester la connexion"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1632
msgid "Test IMAP Connection"
msgstr "Tester la connexion IMAP"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1634
msgid ""
"Connects to the configured mailbox and reports the total and unseen message "
"count."
msgstr ""
"Se connecte à la boîte aux lettres configurée et indique le nombre total de "
"messages et de messages non lus."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1638
msgid "Poll inbox now"
msgstr "Interroger la boîte de réception maintenant"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1643
msgid "Poll Inbox Now"
msgstr "Interroger la boîte de réception maintenant"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1645
msgid ""
"Fetches unseen messages immediately without waiting for WP-Cron. Then click "
"\"Process Pending Queue\" to run the AI pipeline."
msgstr ""
"Récupère immédiatement les messages non lus sans attendre WP-Cron. Cliquez "
"ensuite sur « Traiter la file d’attente en attente » pour exécuter le "
"pipeline IA."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1649
msgid "Process queue"
msgstr "Traiter la file d’attente"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1654
msgid "Process Pending Queue"
msgstr "Traiter la file d’attente en attente"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1656
msgid ""
"Immediately runs the AI pipeline on all pending queue items without waiting "
"for WP-Cron. Use this to test the end-to-end flow after a poll."
msgstr ""
"Exécute immédiatement le pipeline IA sur tous les éléments en attente de la "
"file, sans attendre WP-Cron. Utilisez cela pour tester le flux de bout en "
"bout après un sondage."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1660
msgid "Force reprocess"
msgstr "Forcer le retraitement"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1665
msgid "Force Reprocess Inbox"
msgstr "Forcer le retraitement de la boîte de réception"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1667
msgid ""
"Resets failed/stuck/orphaned queue rows back to pending, then immediately "
"polls for unprocessed messages. Then click \"Process Pending Queue\" to run "
"the AI pipeline. Already-published artworks with valid posts are never re-"
"processed."
msgstr ""
"Réinitialise les lignes de file d’attente échouées/bloquées/orphelines à "
"l’état en attente, puis interroge immédiatement les messages non traités. "
"Cliquez ensuite sur « Traiter la file d’attente en attente » pour exécuter "
"le pipeline IA. Les œuvres déjà publiées avec des articles valides ne sont "
"jamais retraitées."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1697
msgid "Deliverability"
msgstr "Délivrabilité"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1699
msgid ""
"A diagnostic check only — nothing here changes how mail is sent. On ordinary"
" hosting (PHP mail(), no SMTP plugin), mail sent from an address that "
"doesn't match your site's own domain, or from a domain with no SPF/DMARC "
"record at all, is increasingly likely to land in spam or be rejected "
"outright by large mailbox providers. If any row below looks wrong, the most "
"reliable fix is installing an SMTP-sending plugin (WP Mail SMTP, Post SMTP, "
"FluentSMTP, and others all work) configured against a real transactional "
"mail provider, and adding SPF/DMARC records for the domain you send from at "
"your DNS host."
msgstr ""
"Il s’agit uniquement d’un contrôle de diagnostic — rien ici ne modifie la "
"manière dont le courrier est envoyé. Sur un hébergement standard (PHP "
"mail(), sans plugin SMTP), les e-mails envoyés depuis une adresse qui ne "
"correspond pas au domaine de votre site, ou depuis un domaine sans "
"enregistrement SPF/DMARC du tout, ont de plus en plus de chances d’atterrir "
"dans les spams ou d’être rejetés purement et simplement par les grands "
"fournisseurs de boîtes mail. Si une des lignes ci-dessous vous semble "
"incorrecte, la solution la plus fiable consiste à installer un plugin "
"d’envoi SMTP (WP Mail SMTP, Post SMTP, FluentSMTP et d’autres fonctionnent),"
" configuré avec un véritable fournisseur de messagerie transactionnelle, "
"puis à ajouter des enregistrements SPF/DMARC pour le domaine d’envoi chez "
"votre hébergeur DNS."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1705
msgid "From identity"
msgstr "Identité d’envoi"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1706
msgid "Domain matches site?"
msgstr "Le domaine correspond-il au site ?"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1707
msgid "SPF record"
msgstr "Enregistrement SPF"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1708
msgid "DMARC record"
msgstr "Enregistrement DMARC"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1724
msgid "SMTP plugin"
msgstr "Plugin SMTP"

#. translators: %s: detected plugin name, e.g. "WP Mail SMTP"
#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1731
#, php-format
msgid "Detected: %s"
msgstr "Détecté : %s"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1736
msgid ""
"None of the common SMTP-sending plugins were detected — this site is likely "
"relying on PHP's built-in mail(), which most hosts deliver poorly through."
msgstr ""
"Aucun des plugins courants d’envoi SMTP n’a été détecté — ce site s’appuie "
"probablement sur la fonction mail() intégrée de PHP, que la plupart des "
"hébergeurs acheminent mal."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1746
msgid "Send a real test email to:"
msgstr "Envoyer un véritable e-mail de test à :"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1748 includes/Admin/Settings.php:2513
#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:2645
msgid "Send Test"
msgstr "Envoyer le test"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1751
msgid ""
"Sends one plain-text email from the same community identity used for "
"review/vote/vouch mail. Reaching your inbox is a good sign; landing in spam "
"or not arriving at all confirms a real deliverability problem regardless of "
"what the checks above say."
msgstr ""
"Envoie un e-mail en texte brut depuis la même identité de communauté "
"utilisée pour les e-mails de revue/vote/soutien. S’il arrive dans votre "
"boîte de réception, c’est bon signe ; s’il arrive en spam ou n’arrive pas du"
" tout, cela confirme un vrai problème de délivrabilité, quels que soient les"
" résultats des vérifications ci-dessus."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1760
msgid "Found"
msgstr "Trouvé"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1761
msgid "Not found"
msgstr "Non trouvé"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1762
msgid "DNS lookup failed"
msgstr "Échec de la recherche DNS"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1763
msgid "Unavailable on this host"
msgstr "Indisponible sur cet hébergeur"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1770
msgid "No address configured"
msgstr "Aucune adresse configurée"

#. translators: %s: site name
#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1797
#, php-format
msgid "[TEST] Deliverability check from %s"
msgstr "[TEST] Contrôle de délivrabilité depuis %s"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1800
msgid ""
"This is a one-off deliverability test from your Agnosis Settings → Email "
"Inbox page. If you're reading this in your inbox (not spam), the "
"community/transactional From identity is deliverable to this address."
msgstr ""
"Il s’agit d’un test de délivrabilité ponctuel depuis votre page Agnosis "
"Réglages → Boîte de réception des e-mails. Si vous lisez ce message dans "
"votre boîte de réception (et non dans les spams), l’identité d’envoi "
"communautaire/transactionnelle est bien distribuable à cette adresse."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1852
msgid "Pending Applications"
msgstr "Candidatures en attente"

#. translators: %d: number of applications awaiting email confirmation
#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1860
#, php-format
msgid ""
"%d application is awaiting email confirmation from the applicant and isn't "
"listed below yet."
msgid_plural ""
"%d applications are awaiting email confirmation from the applicant and "
"aren't listed below yet."
msgstr[0] ""
"%d candidature attend la confirmation par e-mail du candidat et n’est pas "
"encore listée ci-dessous."
